parameters:
\SE[0]You seem to be in a good mood. \!\SE[0]Did
something good happen?

\SE[59]Well, it's not really something good... \SE[55]More
like, all my problems suddenly vanished and I can't help but
smile... \SE[38]I feel so happy...

\SE[2]You've been through a lot, haven't you? \SE[37]You
should enjoy this momentary happiness.

\SE[2]Oh, did you finish your work? \.Then let's eat some
sweets together.
\SE[16]Hehe, thank you. \SE[0]Well then, may I join you?

\SE[2]By the way, there's something I've been curious
about...
\SE[1] Zero Moon Laura... What is that?

\SE[29]O-Oh, you noticed... \!\SE[62]It seems like I'm being
called that... But I don't remember anything about it...
\SE[44]I wouldn't say I know... more like...

\SE[17]Here they come... the culprit! \SE[15]Now, spill
everything!! \SE[16]I know all the secrets!!

\SE[0]Zero Moon Laura... What is that? \SE[0]It became
famous without me knowing, so I was curious. \SE[2]Does Vega
know something?

\SE[50]Ah... So that's what you're talking about.
\SE[19]Very well. The day has finally come for me to tell
this story...

\SE[52]Oh, that's right... \SE[3]It goes back to around half
a year ago when you became bedridden... \SE[2]We were taking
on various requests at that time.

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you know... she drinks a lot of water while
studying, so she goes to the bathroom... quite frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
